ActCanada Pension Plan Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of JACKSON TAI of Greenwich, Connecticut, United States of America, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of Michael Goldberg, effective June 1, 2016.
